Rubocop: Style/SymbolProc  - Pass &:to_sym as an argument to map instead of a block  - Pass &:capitalize as an argument to select instead of a block  - Pass &:to_s as an argument to map instead of a block
Rubocop: Style/NegatedIf  - Favor unless over if for negative conditions
Rubocop: Style/SpaceBeforeBlockBraces Rubocop: Style/SpaceInsideBlockBraces
Rubocop: Style/SpaceAfterComma  - Space missing after comma
Rubocop: Style/EmptyLinesAroundClassBody  - Extra empty line detected at class body end
Rubocop: Style/HashSyntax  - Use hash rockets syntax
Rubocop: Performance/StringReplacement  - Use delete! instead of gsub!  - Use tr instead of gsub
Rubocop: Style/DeprecatedHashMethods  - Hash#has_key? is deprecated in favor of Hash#key? Add method `key?` to Drop
Rubocop: Style/PercentLiteralDelimiters  - %w-literals should be delimited by ( and ) Rubocop: Style/WordArray  - Use %w or %W for array of words
Rubocop: Style/AndOr  - Use && instead of and  - Use || instead of or
Rubocop: Style/SpecialGlobalVars  - Prefer $LOAD_PATH over $:
Use select and find instead of conditional loop
Rubocop: Style/LineEndConcatenation  - Use \ instead of + or << to concatenate those strings
Rubocop: Style/Semicolon  - Do not use semicolons to terminate expressions
Rubocop: Style/EmptyLiteral  - Use array literal [] instead of Array.new  - Use hash literal {} instead of Hash.new
Further refine our Rubocop to the current styles.
Escape html from site.title and page.title
Update copyright notices to 2016 [ci skip]
Move around CodeClimate so people can do `bundle exec rubocop`.
Be consistent with your hashes and arrays.
Reduce our surface, extend self is useful for some modules.
Added content on relative permalinks
